re":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:48:57.000Z","msg":"自己煮個日特別容易飽"},{"pid":"81f9635a9f2db26cf7c712f3890012824f692606","tid":747443,"uid":186961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:21:01.000Z","msg":"唔係喎，通常一路煮一路試味偷食，<br />\n特別快飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57df0f9becb759994a01eb102fccaca18d9560b","tid":747443,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"因為難食"},{"pid":"9a0246ea140b46a75fef4effe393acae38944566","tid":747443,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"煮飯要出力，要食多啲補充返"},{"pid":"ca671e47e84b8900b4496db6c2b056f1d03f8972","tid":747443,"uid":39274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"因為食完仲要洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e1c175ec02abe35d57e08c39bfa8f33a66d6b2","tid":747443,"uid":44415,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:42:20.000Z","msg":"自己煮先易飽<br />\n因為煮完根本食都唔想食<br />\n成個人俾個爐照到㷫恰恰 乜胃口都冇曬"},{"pid":"3e0118e8789ebf28129de1a175d35036f59f5ac1","tid":747443,"uid":191510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:49:43.000Z","msg":"次次自己煮都食到頂胃<br />\n<br />\n利申:只食意粉"},{"pid":"ebcaff2b8aea1ae9a9fffe44b44e99d4bf667e9b","tid":747443,"uid":195438,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"可能真係菜式同油嘅問題。<br />\n因為自己煮想健康啲，所以多數都落半羹油，豬肉都只係買瘦肉。<br />\n有時炆豬肉一定要買五花腩，會飽好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仲有意粉都係好飽。"},{"pid":"90362a8f2661b73135b70adb385960f087db0d85","tid":747443,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:01:52.000Z","msg":"真係諗唔明，點解唔飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日晏晝1點係食白切雞飯，只係一隻雞脾仔，食完只係食咗兩啖飯，飽到6點<br />\n啱啱煮飯係買咗30蚊五花腩，炒半個椰菜，食咗兩碗飯<br />\n6點半食，依家已經有啲餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人分析到點解會咁"},{"pid":"27ffac835fb86b44f65bf2cd893cd159587c4000","tid":747443,"uid":10788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:24:07.000Z","msg":"自己整要扣體力"}]}